## 📚 예제: 완전한 Hello World

### 프리랭 소스 (Phase B에서 작성)
```freelang
fn main() {
  println("Hello, World!")
}
```

### 컴파일된 바이트코드 (16진수)
```
464C5056 0100 0000          # Header
0000001E 0000001C          # Code size=30, offset=28
01 01 02 0D 48 65 6C 6C   # PUSH "Hello, World!" (string ref)
6F 2C 20 57 6F 72 6C 64    # String data
21 00 60 61 00             # PRINT, HALT 0
0000000A 0000003E          # Data size=10, offset=62
01 00 00 00 00 00 00 03    # Global: i64 = 3
00000001 0000004A          # Symbol count=1
01 04 6D 61 69 6E 00 00    # Function "main"
00 1C 00 00 00 08          # Address=0x1C, Size=8
```

### 실행
```
Input:  bytecode file (16 bytes)
VM:     Loads and executes
Output: "Hello, World!"
```

